{"tid":1997249,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"【5.1撐黃店】黃金周多間黃店現人龍 提供優惠店達2000間（圖輯）","createTime":"2020-05-01T13:55:27.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-02T08:43:29.000Z","uid":25558,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"951bbfc880c2bcd436c78e4aa57b68c9576dcf6e","tid":1997249,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:55:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200501/GWUFRIOMX75KMCWZKKF46WJROE/?code=5eac1e371ba4be008ea4c8e0&amp;clientId=40881634-71a1-414f-9b4f-42563ca4adcf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200501%2FGWUFRIOMX75KMCWZKKF46WJROE%2F%3Fcode%3D5eac1e371ba4be008ea4c8e0%26clientId%3D40881634-71a1-414f-9b4f-42563ca4adcf&d=29ui5Tvv6aczeWgqk0vw10HQxt1T4ELL4DwIHxiqIsg%3D&h=a20c94f1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2F20200501%2FGWUFRIOMX75KMCWZKKF46WJROE%2F%3Fcode%3D5eac1e371ba4be008ea4c8e0%26clientId%3D40881634-71a1-414f-9b4f-42563ca4adcf&h=4a2f06bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/lifestyle/20200501/GWUFRIOMX75KMCWZKKF46WJROE/?code=5eac1e371ba4be008ea4c8e0&amp;clientId=40881634-71a1-414f-9b4f-42563ca4adcf</a><br />\n<br />\n【5.1撐黃店】黃金周多間黃店現人龍 提供優惠店達2000間（圖輯）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588323931_1399.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588323931_1399.jpg&h=616a9827&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有網民號召在五一黃金周「懲罰」黃店， 幫襯並在網上平台打卡，建立屬於真&bull;香港人的「五一黃金周」，壯大黃色經濟圈。而多個民間團體聯合舉行「黃金周支援黃店計劃」，最後招攬達2000間店舖參與，有關商戶在長假期間為顧客提供不同優惠，如提供折扣、購物免運費等，亦有要商戶會指市民高舉「五」、「一」手勢，或叫出「黑警死全家」等口號，便可獲得優惠。<br />\n<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n記者們行走多區，發現多間黃店現長長人龍，有市民指，「呢個（黃金周）會取代勞動節」 、「好開心，有好多黃店揀，終於有屬於香港人嘅節日」、「今日真係有光復香港嘅感覺」，不過亦有人不忘提醒要分散投資，「懲罰」生意較少的黃店，以及除了食店外的其他種類黃店。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n記者：飲食組<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以Pepe蛋糕為名的西環華爾登餅店，也有不少市民購買蛋糕支持小店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588327514_26dc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588327514_26dc.jpg&h=34dfee90&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n北角人人和平小飯店內，全場滿座。<br />\n<br />\n滔滔甜品西環店亦全場爆滿，有市民在店外輪候。<br />\n<br />\n西營盤小店茶咖里，門外出現人龍，需要排隊等候入座。<br />\n<br />\n下午時份，咖啡店Brew Note門外也有市民排隊「懲罰」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588323931_720c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588323931_720c.jpg&h=0e58600f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n黃之鋒亦有去支持北角活一鮮。<br />\n<br />\n旺角有照相及影印店響應5.1黃金周，提供指定服務八折優惠，希望大家支持食店以外的黃店。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588320233_58e4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588320233_58e4.jpg&h=b15010a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於九龍灣的釜之魂釜飯專門店。<br />\n<br />\n位於西九文化區的Rest Coffee Gin（唞唞），門外出現人龍。<br />\n<br />\n有茶飲店門前圍滿排隊食客，店員亦加快手腳處理訂單。<br />\n<br />\n龍門冰室（銅鑼灣分店）午餐時間現人龍。<br />\n<br />\n葵涌快餐店OH MY DOG 生意爆升，大批食客落柯打買外賣漢堡包。<br />\n<br />\n大埔和拉麵大約需要等半小時才入座。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588320235_73ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588320235_73ce.jpg&h=5baf079f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n大埔暢和麵家只有約十多個座位，不少人不介意在走廊等候。<br />\n<br />\n之前因粟米斑腩飯被海關票控的鼎天茶室，亦全場爆滿。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20200501/large/1588320237_9e44.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20200501%2Flarge%2F1588320237_9e44.jpg&h=5230b03a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n葵廣有眾多黃店，得到不少人排隊支持。<br />\n<br />\n和暢金廚提供$50午市優惠。<br />\n<br />\n觀塘工廈內亦有不少人支持黃店。"},{"pid":"2718b505e7ba9fba60658e13468efb3123e4094f","tid":1997249,"uid":44358,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-01T13:59:43.000Z","msg":"我就係要呢啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"942cd783d860b8de4d1577a166c740e543caa714","tid":1997249,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-02T08:43:29.000Z","msg":"借位一用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n溫馨提示提提大家<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">西樹泡芙係藍</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日見到超級多後生女排買二送二個優惠<br />\n可能有啲人未知<br />\n但希望如果知道嘅人以後搵其他嘢取代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n買西樹泡芙之前可否停一停諗一諗?<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1739594\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1739594</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"}]}